[SN]TITLE[SN]
Christian Benteke, Antonio Conte, Olympic Stadium - West Ham gossip

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
West Ham chairman David Sullivan says the club would be keen to sign Liverpool striker Christian Benteke but admits the Belgian's wages would be a major stumbling block. (Mirror)

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
West Ham have submitted a planning application for a the largest digital screens in Europe - measuring 83m x 12m - to be wrapped around the outside of the Olympic Stadium. (West Ham FC)
The Upton Park club were keen to recruit Chelsea-bound coach Antonio Conte after Sam Allardyce's departure last summer. (Gazzetta World)
